## Docker Configuration

### Individual Service Dockerfile (Example: Student Service)

```dockerfile
FROM node:18-alpine

WORKDIR /app

# Copy package files
COPY package*.json ./

# Install dependencies
RUN npm ci --only=production

# Copy source code
COPY . .

# Expose port
EXPOSE 5002

# Health check
HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
  CMD node -e "require('http').get('http://localhost:5002/health', (r) => {process.exit(r.statusCode === 200 ? 0 : 1)})"

# Start service
CMD ["node", "src/server.js"]
```

### Docker Compose Development (`docker-compose.dev.yml`)

```yaml
version: '3.8'

services:
  # MySQL Database
  mysql:
    image: mysql:8.0
    environment:
      MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD: rootpassword
    ports:
      - "3306:3306"
    volumes:
      - mysql_data:/var/lib/mysql
      - ./init-scripts:/docker-entrypoint-initdb.d
    networks:
      - sms_network
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD", "mysqladmin", "ping", "-h", "localhost"]
      interval: 10s
      timeout: 5s
      retries: 5

  # Auth Service
  auth-service:
    build: ./services/auth-service
    ports:
      - "5001:5001"
    environment:
      NODE_ENV: development
      PORT: 5001
      DB_HOST: mysql
      DB_USER: root
      DB_PASSWORD: rootpassword
      DB_NAME: auth_db
      JWT_SECRET: your_jwt_secret_key_here
      JWT_EXPIRES_IN: 24h
    depends_on:
      mysql:
        condition: service_healthy
    networks:
      - sms_network
    volumes:
      - ./services/auth-service:/app
      - /app/node_modules

  # Student Service
  student-service:
    build: ./services/student-service
    ports:
      - "5002:5002"
    environment:
      NODE_ENV: development
      PORT: 5002
      DB_HOST: mysql
      DB_USER: root
      DB_PASSWORD: rootpassword
      DB_NAME: student_db
      AUDIT_SERVICE_URL: http://audit-service:5005
    depends_on:
      mysql:
        condition: service_healthy
    networks:
      - sms_network
    volumes:
      - ./services/student-service:/app
      - /app/node_modules

  # Course Service
  course-service:
    build: ./services/course-service
    ports:
      - "5003:5003"
    environment:
      NODE_ENV: development
      PORT: 5003
      DB_HOST: mysql
      DB_USER: root
      DB_PASSWORD: rootpassword
      DB_NAME: course_db
    depends_on:
      mysql:
        condition: service_healthy
    networks:
      - sms_network
    volumes:
      - ./services/course-service:/app
      - /app/node_modules

  # Enrollment Service
  enrollment-service:
    build: ./services/enrollment-service
    ports:
      - "5004:5004"
    environment:
      NODE_ENV: development
      PORT: 5004
      DB_HOST: mysql
      DB_USER: root
      DB_PASSWORD: rootpassword
      DB_NAME: enrollment_db
      STUDENT_SERVICE_URL: http://student-service:5002
      COURSE_SERVICE_URL: http://course-service:5003
      AUDIT_SERVICE_URL: http://audit-service:5005
    depends_on:
      mysql:
        condition: service_healthy
      student-service:
        condition: service_started
      course-service:
        condition: service_started
    networks:
      - sms_network
    volumes:
      - ./services/enrollment-service:/app
      - /app/node_modules

  # Audit Service
  audit-service:
    build: ./services/audit-service
    ports:
      - "5005:5005"
    environment:
      NODE_ENV: development
      PORT: 5005
      DB_HOST: mysql
      DB_USER: root
      DB_PASSWORD: rootpassword
      DB_NAME: audit_db
    depends_on:
      mysql:
        condition: service_healthy
    networks:
      - sms_network
    volumes:
      - ./services/audit-service:/app
      - /app/node_modules

  # API Gateway
  api-gateway:
    build: ./api-gateway
    ports:
      - "3000:3000"
    environment:
      NODE_ENV: development
      PORT: 3000
      AUTH_SERVICE_URL: http://auth-service:5001
      STUDENT_SERVICE_URL: http://student-service:5002
      COURSE_SERVICE_URL: http://course-service:5003
      ENROLLMENT_SERVICE_URL: http://enrollment-service:5004
      AUDIT_SERVICE_URL: http://audit-service:5005
      JWT_SECRET: your_jwt_secret_key_here
    depends_on:
      - auth-service
      - student-service
      - course-service
      - enrollment-service
      - audit-service
    networks:
      - sms_network
    volumes:
      - ./api-gateway:/app
      - /app/node_modules

  # Frontend
  frontend:
    build: ./frontend
    ports:
      - "5173:5173"
    environment:
      VITE_API_URL: http://localhost:3000/api
    depends_on:
      - api-gateway
    networks:
      - sms_network
    volumes:
      - ./frontend:/app
      - /app/node_modules

volumes:
  mysql_data:

networks:
  sms_network:
    driver: bridge
```

---

## API Endpoints (via API Gateway)

All requests go through API Gateway at `http://localhost:3000`

### Authentication

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required |
|--------|----------|-------------|---------------|
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Administrator login | No |
| POST | `/api/auth/logout` | Administrator logout | Yes |
| GET | `/api/auth/verify` | Verify JWT token | Yes |

### Students

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required |
|--------|----------|-------------|---------------|
| GET | `/api/students` | Get all students (paginated) | Yes |
| GET | `/api/students/:id` | Get student by ID | Yes |
| POST | `/api/students` | Create new student | Yes |
| PUT | `/api/students/:id` | Update student | Yes |
| DELETE | `/api/students/:id` | Delete student | Yes |

### Courses

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required |
|--------|----------|-------------|---------------|
| GET | `/api/courses` | Get all courses | Yes |
| GET | `/api/courses/:id` | Get course by ID | Yes |
| POST | `/api/courses` | Create new course | Yes |
| PUT | `/api/courses/:id` | Update course | Yes |
| DELETE | `/api/courses/:id` | Delete course | Yes |

### Enrollments

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required |
|--------|----------|-------------|---------------|
| GET | `/api/enrollments` | Get all enrollments | Yes |
| GET | `/api/enrollments/student/:studentId` | Get student enrollments (course history) | Yes |
| POST | `/api/enrollments` | Enroll student in course | Yes |
| PUT | `/api/enrollments/:id` | Update enrollment | Yes |
| DELETE | `/api/enrollments/:id` | Remove enrollment | Yes |

### Audit Logs

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required |
|--------|----------|-------------|---------------|
| GET | `/api/audit-logs` | Get all audit logs (filtered) | Yes |
| GET | `/api/audit-logs/student/:studentId` | Get logs for student | Yes |
| GET | `/api/audit-logs/admin/:adminId` | Get logs for admin | Yes |

