## Implementation Phases

### Phase 1: Infrastructure Setup (Week 1)
- [ ] Create project structure for all services
- [ ] Setup Docker and Docker Compose
- [ ] Initialize MySQL with all databases
- [ ] Create base Express app for each service
- [ ] Configure environment variables
- [ ] Setup Git repository with proper structure

### Phase 2: Core Services (Week 2-3)
- [ ] **Auth Service**: Authentication, JWT generation
- [ ] **Student Service**: Student CRUD, degree programs
- [ ] **Course Service**: Course management
- [ ] **Enrollment Service**: Enrollment logic, inter-service calls
- [ ] **Audit Service**: Audit logging endpoint

### Phase 3: API Gateway (Week 3)
- [ ] Setup API Gateway with routing
- [ ] Implement authentication middleware
- [ ] Add rate limiting
- [ ] Configure CORS
- [ ] Setup health checks

### Phase 4: Frontend (Week 4-5)
- [ ] Initialize React project
- [ ] Implement authentication flow
- [ ] Build student management interface
- [ ] Create course management UI
- [ ] Implement enrollment interface
- [ ] Add audit log viewer

### Phase 5: Testing & Integration (Week 6)
- [ ] Unit tests for each service
- [ ] Integration tests
- [ ] End-to-end testing
- [ ] Performance testing
- [ ] Security audit

### Phase 6: Deployment (Week 7)
- [ ] Production Docker setup
- [ ] Kubernetes manifests (optional)
- [ ] CI/CD pipeline
- [ ] Monitoring and logging
- [ ] Documentation

